result.execSummary:
All charges against Dantony R. Chamblis in this case have been dismissed. These charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Dantony R. Chamblis is presumed innocent.

For more information, see Wisconsin Statute 111.335 and the Department of Workforce Development's publication, Arrest and Conviction Records under the Law.
